inn1.comm: pretty sharp inward movement straightaway by Praveen, nips back in as well. Hafeez managed to fend it off, just
sharp movement again, this time it catches Hafeez on the pads but missing leg
nips back in and Hafeez defends with soft hands
he errs by giving him width and Hafeez punishes it, he has to stretch out and cut that past point
loses control and drifts down the leg side
much better, in the channel around the off stump, he knocks it back to the bowler
hits a good length and he mistimes it to midwicket
gentle movement away from the left-hander, not much pace and Jamshed was happy to leave it
sharper movement away from the batsman and Jamshed didn't offer a shot again
fuller in length on the pads and he clips it down to fine leg, Dinda picks up
too full and wide and he reaches out and pushes it just wide of cover
teases him with late away movement, Jamshed had to play at it and the ball nearly shaved the face of the bat
gets beside the line and deftly angles it down to point
stays over the wicket to the left-hander, lands it outside off and straightens to the keeper
punched off the back foot down to short cover
the timing was exquisite there, not a bad delivery, length ball on middle and he just clipped it wide of midwicket, didn't hit it too hard, maintained his balance
and another in the same area! Fuller delivery this time and Jamshed bent forward slightly, clipped it with the movement wide of mid-on
stays back at the crease and defends back to the bowler
Praveen struggles with his line as he once again strays down the leg side, he moves across and clips it down to the vacant spaces at fine leg
keeps it on the off stump and he clips it down to midwicket
grants him width and he bends his knee to steer it past cover point, but he can't beat the fielder
the sight of the packed off-side field doesn't deter him as he uses  the width, bends is knee and easily steers it past the gap at cover, super placement
moves it away from the right-hander and he leaves it alone
skids through and hits his pads but that was missing leg
drifts on the pads and he flicks it uppishly down to fine leg, seeing too many balls on  the pads today
lovely delivery, good one by Dinda, pitched up and draws Hafeez forward on the drive and beats him
gets across and pushes it straight to the bowler
gets across and punches it straight to mid-off
hits the deck hard and he has Hafeez ducking under that bouncer, good delivery
stays back and punches it down to Praveen at mid-off and Jamshed responded to the call early
gets half forward and jusy manages to squeeze it past backward point, he gets a hand to it and  third man picks up
goes back at the crease and punches it down to cover point
lots of away movement and driven very firmly but straight to Rohit at short cover, that stung his right hand
too straight and on the body, he clips him behind square on the on side
short of a length outside off and he steers it wide of point
punched just wide of the bowler and Irfan dives, Yusuf does well to slide at mid-on to stop it
he punched it straight back to the bowler
just short of a length and he chops it down to point
Dinda continues over the wicket, Jamshed punches it straight to cover
goes back at the crease and he clips it down to midwicket
that's a very sharp bouncer but unfortunately for the bowler he is penalised, Dhoni just about catches it
angles it across the left-hander and he pushes it down to cover
stays beside the line and pushes it down to point
gets away with a full delivery as Jamshed can only drive straight to point
one-handed but good enough! Short delivery and Hafeez released his right hand on the pull over midwicket, had more than enough to reach the rope
good length on the off stump and he drives him down to cover
excellent stop by Tiwary at point, driven on the front foot, Tiwary is on for Tendulkar but I don't know why
bowls it straighter and he punches it down the track
comes half forward and punches it down to mid-off
whips it to Gambhir who's a bit deep at mid-on
fullish in length and pushed down towards short cover
uppishly flicked away and right in the gap, looked a bit risky at first though, Dinda errs by pitching it up on the pads
fullish on the off stump this time and pushed down to mid-off
gets half forward and he pushes it wide of cover point
punched just wide of mid-off for a quick single, Tendulkar's back on the field now
length ball on the off stump and left alone
opportunity missed by Hafeez, wide delivery and he ends up chopping it to short cover
punched wide of mid-off and they risk a sharp single,  Yusuf's throw was wide of the stumps
the attempted yorker turns into a low full toss, Jamshed comes well forward and drives it firmly past cover point, picks the narrow gap between two fielders
gets beside the line and steers it to point
just opens the face and dabs it down towards third man for a single
Hafeez walks down the pitch to unsettle the bowler, he picks it from the off stump and forcefully clips it away wide of square leg, beats the fielder at the deep
pushed down to long on for one
he tries to back away and cut, to a tossed up length ball, misses
much fuller and he gets the front foot out to ease it to long on
picks it up from outside off and paddles it fine of fine leg
stays back and punches down to long off
comes down the track, Raina pushes it through flat and into the batsman, who manages to tuck it through square for two
flighted and full, an easy push down to long off
nudged to midwicket, Jamshed takes off, Hafeez sees Raina has too, towards the ball, and sends back his partner
punched to long on from the crease
well done, Rohit saves one with a dive to his right, parries the drive towards extra cover
makes room outside leg and tries to drive through extra cover, mistimes it
guided through point
comes in with the angle, bit of an inside edge as it rolls to fine leg
makes room and punches the shortish ball, gets it wide of sweeper cover
short, too short, Hafeez goes back and pulls, but ends up hitting into the ground
shows a straight bat to a pitched up ball and gets it past Raina to long on
opens the face and squeezes out another single, to deep point
could have been close, he backed away to a fullish ball on the stumps, and just got his bat down in time to steer to short third man
gets down on his knee and sweeps powerfully to fine leg

scrambling, lunging, desperate slide from Dinda at deep point, he gets a hand to the ball, it rolls away off his feet and by the time he recovers to get it back, it has touched the rope, a fine cut shot by Jamshed
appeal for lbw as he misses the sweep to a tossed up ball, pitching in leg and probably going down leg, well, no, replays show it would have hit leg stump, hmm
further down leg with the angle, this time he gets the sweep down to fine leg
Hafeez laps the sweep from off stump, Dinda cuts it off this time at fine leg
pulled away through square leg
gets well forward and pushes it towards point
tossed up on middle and leg, he clips him down to long-on
steers it in front of point and takes an easy single
another easy single taken to the infield on the off side, putting pressure on the fielders
gets well forward and drives straight to mid-off
tossed up on the off stump and driven to sweeper cover
gives him a bit of width but Hafeez ends up stabbing it back to the bowler
full outside the off stump and driven to sweeper cover, Gambhir there
goes back at the crease and punches it down towards cover point
tucks him up for room and he punches it down to point
drifts on the pads and he gets an inside edge to square leg
forcefully whipped away but straight to midwicket, Dinda bowling a tighter line today
Jamshed made a bit of room exposed the stumps, waited for the turn and punched it hard past cover, well played
strays down the leg side
excellent fielding by Dinda at fine leg, forcefully swept past short fine leg and Dinda sweeping on the leg side gave it everything and cut it off before the rope
round the wicket to the right-hander, he clips it down to midwicket
commits to the sweep and he places it to the leg side
goes back, waits for the turn and clips it to the on side
stays back and clips it firmly down towards deep midwicket
Dinda shouldn't beat himself up for this because this was mighty close to the stumps! The ball kept low and the inside edge sneaked past the leg stump and beat short fine leg
driven on the up but past the big gap at point and that's a fifty for the Prof!
now Jamshed brings up his fifty! Solidly clipped close to the pads, uses his wrists well and Gambhir does a cross-country run from deep square leg and dives in vain
the short ball hurries on him and he fails to time it, the ball drops in front of square leg
gives him width and he slams it down to sweeper cover
close call for Jamshed! Another sharp bouncer and he was in no position to pull with authority, top edge falls wide of square leg, wide of any fielder
Jamshed makes room and exposes his stumps and Irfan follows him and yet bowls it wide down the leg side
drifts on the pads and he clips it straight to Dinda at fine leg
reaches forward and drives wide of mid-off, Praveen slides
stays beside the line and angles it down to third man
he had the fine leg up and yet fed him a delivery down the leg stump, Hafeez swivels and works it on its way and well wide of Tendulkar at short fine leg, Irfan isn't pleased with himself
goes the other way this time! Too wide from Irfan and Hafeez plays a neat square cut off the front foot wide of backward point
punches it down to mid-off for a single
tossed up on middle and leg and clipped down to midwicket
clipped behind square and Raina slides and cuts it off
bowls it flatter and Jamshed punches it down to mid-on
hint of turn and he clips it against the turn
gets forward and softly knocks it back to the bowler
clipped straight to midwicket, better over for India
tossed up outside off and driven down to long-off
makes a bit of room and chops it down to cover
makes room, the ball skids through and he gently steers it square on the off side
goes back at he crease and knocks it down to long-on
fires it a bit full and he squeezes it out just wide of the bowler
works it down to mid-on and another single
makes room and cuts down to point
makes room and pulls but finds mid-on
bowls it flat and short and Jamshed was ready for that, rocked back and pulled wide of Tendulkar at mid-on
gets a thin outside edge down to third man
makes room and he cuts just wide of Irfan at third man
punched down to long-on and they jog the single
Jamshed makes room to sweep and Yusuf followed him and still sprayed it wide down the leg side
worked to the deep on the on side
makes room and gently dabs it down to point
clipped towards short mid-on and the fielder flicked it to the bowler's end and Hafeez had to dive
full on the pads and clipped to midwicket
tossed up on the pads and clipped to the deep on the on side
tossed up  and loops to the batsman, gets on his knee and sweeps
goes back and clips him down towards deep midwicket
long hop and he punishes it, leg spinner from round the wicket, rocks back, clears his back leg and pulls wide of midwicket
tossed up down the leg side and he sweeps but short fine leg picks up
flighted on the pads and clipped down to midwicket
bowls round the wicket, tries to sweep but ends up inside edging to thje pad
tried to slice that past third man
gets well forward and clips it down to square leg
flatter delivery and clipped down to deep midwicket
drops it short again and he stays back and pulls down to Irfan at wide long-on
tossed up on the pads and clipped to square leg for the single to bring up the 150, very ominous signs for India. These two have been quite reletless
tossed up down the leg side and he sweeps and Praveen does well to slide at fine leg
makes room and whips it against the turn to midwicket
stays back and works it down to deep square leg

Dropped: Tendulkar wasn't expecting that at all, full ball, Jamshed knocks it back to Tendulkar with force, he stuck his hand out and the ball deflected a long way to the off side, indicative of the power behind the shot, he's in pain and the physio is out
makes room and steers it to short third man
claps it down towards sweeper cover
steers it down to point
goes back and punches it down to long-off
punches it back to the bowler
punches it to long-off and he jogs the single
works it down towards square leg for a single
clipped off the pads down to the leg side
gets on his knee and sweeps firmly down to deep square leg
forces a full delivery down to long-on
fullish on middle and leg and he works it to wide long-on
makes a bit of room and drills it to long-off
flat! Hafeez gets on his knee and slogs him flat and over the reach of deep square leg, good bat speed on that one
clips it to the on side
gets forward and works it down to long-on
makes a lot of room and cuts it wide of point
pushes a low full toss down to long-on
flatter delivery and he forces it down to long-off
full and wide and he square drives it to point
nothing going India's way, wasn't a bad delivery and Jamshed shaped to cut but got a thick outside edge past the keeper and beats third man
chips down the track and checks his shot, dabs it down to third man
angles it towards the left-hander and he works it down to long-on
goes back at the crease and clips him down to deep square leg
clips it down to short midwicket for a quick single
tossed up wide of the leg stump, clips it against the turn to the leg side
smartly played, waited for it and steered it wide of short third man while on the front foot
initially wanted to paddle that but then decided to steer it to short third man, Jamshed was off the blocks quickly, the fielder fumbled
gets on his knee early and sweeps
makes room and cuts him down to sweeper cover,  he's prepared to play it late
stays back and clips it to long-on
fullish on the pads and worked to long-on
clipped straight to midwicket, no chance of a run there
fullish on the pads and worked to long-on, 98 now
gets on his knee early and sweeps fine, fine leg mops up
makes room and Yusuf follows him and Jamshed punches it past the bowler who dives
full on the off stump and pushed to long-off, he will keep the strike, on 99

century No.4 for Hafeez! Pushes a quick single down to mid-off, Ashwin gathered but Hafeez was too quick for him, a century against India will always look good on the CV for a Pakistan cricketer and vice-versa
Jamshed gets forward and pushes a full delivery down to mid-off
forces it wide of deep point for a single
goes back at the crease and pushes it to long-off, that's the 200 up
makes room and slices it down to deep point for a single
bangs it in short and he swivels and pulls him down to deep square leg
goes back at the crease and thumps it down to long-on
full and pushed back to the bowler
tossed up and clipped down to long-on
stays back and whips it against the turn to midwicket, on 98 now
drifts wide down the leg side, quicker delivery
commits forward and gently pushes it to long-on
tossed up on the leg stump and he clips it down to deep square leg
Jamshed gets his maiden ODI century! Clips a full delivery down to wide long-on and he bends down to do the sajda, well played Nasir!
timed that clip really well to deep midwicket, he jogs the single
comes round the wicket, he clips it straight to square leg
audacious! Shows his confidence, Jamshed made room and Praveen followed him, he picked that from wide of the leg stump and deposited that just over the rope at deep square leg
makes room and drills a full toss down to long-on
fuller delivery and he drills it back to the bowler
drops it flat and he makes room and pulls down to deep midwicket
hit on the pads as he tries to sweep and there's an appeal, seems like ages ago since we heard an appeal
makes room and lofts it inside out over cover, top shot
Irfan just manages to hang on! Jamshed gets on his knee and slogs and gets a top edge that swirls towards short third man, Irfan jogs forward and the ball nearly bounces off his palm
stays back and he clips it off the pads
Akmal walks down the pitch, adjusts his shot on seeing the shorter length and dabs it to third man
slower ball and Hafeez didn't read it properly! He was on his knee to slog that away over the on side, the off cutter hits his back leg, you could see off and middle stumps, Gould was convinced
full ball and he squeezes it to the bowler
shorter in length and he pulls it down to deep square leg
short again and this time he opens the face of the bat and steers him down to third man
that's an excellent shot, the field is up, he stays beside the line and slices it in front of square and beats the packed off-side field at cover
ouch! Rohit and Kohli collide, he played it behind square leg and the two fielders converged, Kohli seemed to take the bigger blow, they run four
gets forward and pushes it to the off side
clipped just wide of the bowler
turn and bounce and it hits him high on the pad
clipped to the on side and they can't sneak in a single
he bangs it in short and he pulls it to deep square leg
Akmal  takes control! Length ball on middle and leg and he makes room and pulls over midwicket, nearly a six
good running! He clipped it in front of long-on and called for two as soon as he set off, put pressure on the fielder
Akmal's not done yet in this over! Pitched up delivery on the off stump, Akmal makes room and scoops that over mid-off
the slow leg cutter, he pushes that to the on side
the slower bouncer down the leg side, Younis attempts to pull but misses
clipped down to long-on and that's 14 off the over
clipped down to deep midwicket
continues round the wicket, he stays back and clips him down to deep midwicket
stays back and clips it with the turn to long-on
clipped towards long-on again, shaping to be another big partnership
jogs a single to the leg side
Akmal shapes to cut but the extra bounce beats him, that wasn't too far from the edge too
works it down to long-on
he moves his back leg to distract the bowler, bowls the slower ball and he edges it down to third man
on the off stump and he whips it to long-on
fullish on the off stump and he pushes it to cover
thick leading edge but it clears extra cover, lucky escape there for the batsman
drills a full delivery down to long-off and nearly picks up a boundary, Akmal was too slow with the running there
full on the of stump and forced down to long-off
punched off the back foot but extra cover picks up
that's lovely timing! Angles away from the right-hander and he elegantly slices it past backward point, too wide for third man to cut it off
full on the pads and he clips him down to wide long-on
Akmal tried to paddle it but adjusted well to the full delivery on the off stump, he ended up squeezing it to the off side
whips it to square leg to retain the strike
drills a full ball down to deep midwicket
makes room to a full delivery and he swings and misses
steers it down towards Ashwin at third man, Akmal takes the first run quickly and hurries Younis for the second
backs away to slam it straight but misses it completely
straight to short fine leg! Akmal tries to paddle it away down to fine leg, it's a low full toss swinging in and he ends up scooping it down to Gambhir who didn't have to move much
the milestone will have to wait, he stays back and defends this one
shuffles and clips him down to deep midwicket, gives the strike to Afridi
gets to 7000 ODI runs with a single squeezed out to deep cover
takes a quick single to short midwicket
pushes a full delivery down to long-on, looks like he's setting himself up for something big
drags it shorter, he pulls but keeps it down, deep midwicket picks up
tries to squeeze out a yorker outside off and Dhoni asks the question, he thought he may have edged it
mistimed loft over extra cover and Rohit runs back and tries to catch it on the fall but doesn't time his dive well
inswinger and it's a full toss, he clips it wide of midwicket
full and wide outside the off stump, he makes room and tries to squirt it out
clipped off the pad to the on side and there's an overthrow to the bowler's end
smacks a low full toss wide of long-off, Dinda does well to pick it up so they can only take a single
slower ball and he gently eases it down to third man
good slower ball again, Afridi makes room and angles it down to third man
Irfan totally loses control of that, high full  toss really wide of the off stump, he was attempting the slower ball
good comeback by Irfan, gets his slower ball right this time, can only push it back to the bowler
punches it towards mid-off and hurries the single
another good slower ball by Irfan, on a yorker length and Younis nearly edged it to the keeper, stifled appeal by Dhoni
Irfan pitches it up and it's in the slot for Younis to loft inside out over extra cover, beats the big gap in the deep between two fielders
gets on the front foot and drives down to long-off
fullish delivery and drilled down to long-on
reaches out to a low full toss outside off and he slices it one-handed over point, he seems to have broken his bat
well bowled, on a yorker length and he can only squeeze a single to the off side
scoops a low full toss and it just drops short of long-on, another chip flies off the bat and this time Afridi asks for a new bat
lucky boundary for Pakistan, he swings and gets a thick outside edge that flies past the keeper, third man nowhere in sight, brings up the 300
makes the mistake of bowling the length ball, Younis swivels and pulls off the front foot wide of deep square leg
squeezes out a yorker to Raina at point
sweeps a full delivery down to deep square leg, Praveen was cramping up there so that allowed a third run
bashed down the ground to long-off and he nearly smacked his non-striker along the way
full delivery and he squeezes it out to extra cover
he loses control of that and sprays a high full toss, apologies to Afridi
he picks a full delivery and tries to hoick it over deep midwicket but hits it straight down Kohli's throat, temporary relief for India
squirts out a yorker to point and he was sent back, a direct hit was needed
shows his confidence by moving across and scooping over short fine leg, Dinda chases and just manages to pull it back
swings at a full delivery outside off and misses
drives square on the front foot and Tiwary does really well to slide to his right at point and save at least two
scoops it over extra cover and the ball drops in front of sweeper cover
makes room and lofts inside out just wide of a diving Raina at extra cover, gets to his fifty as well

one of the more unbelievable catches you will see! Younis made room to scoop inside out over extra cover and Raina was at the edge of the circle, leapt and plucked it mid-air with his wrong hand, he was moving to his left so it was that much more difficult for him
gets an inside edge down to deep midwicket
bowls a slower ball really wide of the off stump, Misbah opted not to do anything with it
down the track and he gets a high full toss which he inside edges to the thigh, ouch!
pulls a slower delivery down to deep midwicket and takes a single

India's catching of late should lift their spirits! Azam gets across to the off stump to to slam a slower delivery over the on side, wasn't in full control and Kohli managed to cup it while pedaling backwards, fell back and managed to hang on
forces a full toss down to deep square leg
swishes a slower ball and fails to make contact, they sneak in a bye
Misbah was on all fours when he played that! Another slower ball and he tried to whip that over midwicket, slipped at the crease but managed to gather himself

inn2.comm: tossed up on the off stump and patted back to the bowler
doesn't take long to strike! Tossed up on middle and the ball straightens, Gambhir was trying to work it across the line but was struck in front of middle, easy one for the umpire
goes back and defends back back to the bowler
clips it to the on side
clipped to Misbah at midwicket who midwicket
he gets forward and drives down to long-on
gets a bit of extra bounce and he stays back and defends back to the bowler
sprays it too wide outside the off stump, he was bowling a bit wide of the off stump too
stays beside the line and angles it down towards point, good stop by Hafeez
nips back in and hits him high on the body, 145 kph, Kohli was on the hop trying to whip it away
where did that take off from? Really kicked up off a good length and Akmal tried to catch that but the late movement beat him, deflected off the glove
short and wide and he ended up chopping it to the off side
a leading edge goes for four! Well, not sure what Kohli was trying to do but the extra pace and bounce unsettled him,flies off the leading edge and clears backward point, the outfield did the rest
goes back at the crease and chops it towards point
stays back and punches it wide of cover and sets off for a quick single
classic pull! He reads the length early, goes across and pulls it along the ground past midwicket, really fizzed off the bat
goes back and tucks it behind square on the on side
classic Tendulkar! Fractionally short outside the off stump, bends it back in with the angle, Tendulkar's on his feet as he stylishly slices that wide of cover, two fielders give chase
clipped to the on side with the angle and that's 12 off the over
goes back at the crease and dabs it down to point
goes back and flicks it towards square leg, his signature shot
poor Akmal's having a torrid time already! This one nips back in sharply off a shorter length, sneaks past the inside edge and Akmal falls to his left and can't stop it
stays on the back foot and taps it to the off side
solid punch off the back foot but straight to backward point, the fielder has a shy at the bowler's end
that just flew off the bat, not a bad delivery really, on the body and he shuffled just slightly and whipped it past square leg, the fielder in the deep had no chance
no problems for Akmal there, Cheema gets this one to beat Tendulkar, very nearly takes the edge, good delivery
gets across and taps it back to the bowler
bends it back in and Tendulkar shuffles and clips him wide of mid-on
stays beside the line and taps it down towards cover point
good running by Kohli, he stays on the backfoot and clips it in front of mid-on and calls early
Tendulkar of the old! The upper cut this time, Cheema digs it in short and Tendulkar arches back, rides the bounce and lofts it over slip, just clears the rope
stays beside the line and chops it to the off side
stays beside the line and knocks it towards point again
delivers from slightly wide of the crease, Kohli hops and knocks it to the on side and calls early
not the wisest single! He clipped it towards midwicket and despite taking off quickly he was in trouble, a direct hit was needed
placed it well between cover and extra cover but didn't time it too well, fetched him a couple though
sharp bouncer and the batsman swings at thin air, easily taken by Umar Akmal
just a hint of width to cut but he ended up chopping it towards point
tucks him up for a bit of room and he punches it down to mid-on
bowls it consistently short of a good length, he swivels and clips wide of mid-on
solidly punched off the meat of the bat but straight to extra cover
stays beside the line and angles it down towards point
there's protection in the deep on the on side, he bowls it full on the pads and he works it away neatly down to deep midwicket, the fielder at deep square picks up
drifts on the body and he clips it down to deep square leg
good length on the off stump and he gets across covers the line and knocks it to the on side
stays back at the crease and punches him down towards extra cover
another stylish whip but straight to Hammad Azam at deep backward square leg, takes the first run quickly
sharp bouncer, hurried on Tendulkar only just managed to keep it down, takes a single to the leg side
it was short and wide and very tempting for Tendulkar, he tried to cut but was beaten
grants him width and he punches it wide of extra cover, hit it off the toe of the bat and that brings up the 50
punched down towards mid-on and Hammad Azam runs across and cuts it off
whipped away, Cheema gets a little predictable with his line and length and he went across and worked it past the arc between mid-on and midwicket
punched uppishly through the off side and it beat the diving cover fielder who I think took some pace off the ball
nicely punched off the full face of the bat down to mid-off
this one keeps low and squares him up outside the off stump, could so easily have taken the inside edge, well stopped by Akmal
straightens and he defends that one
gets a leading edge that travels to cover
skids through, he stays back at the crease and knocks it to the on side
Appeal for a stumping! He is safe, the doosra beat Tendulkar outside off, his backfoot was always behind the crease, Akmal wasn't really confident
gets on his knee and plays an authoritative sweep down to deep backward square, Cheema manages to stop it could easily have over-ran the ball
Afridi asks questions straightaway, bowled it flat and the ball trapped him on the pad but down the leg side
Tendulkar wanted to paddle it then at the last second changed his mind and nudged it to third man
stays back and punches it down towards midwicket
stays beside the line and taps it down to cover point
gets well forward and pushes it firmly down to mid-on
clipped wide of midwicket and Kohli called two as soon as he set off, Tendulkar was equal to the task
tossed up on middle and he clips it down to the leg side
flatter delivery and he stays back and punches it down to long-on
stays back and knocks it towards mid-on
works it with the turn to the leg side, easy single
nicely clipped wide of midwicket, effortlessly done
Kohli tried to force that past the covers but got an inside edge onto his boot
works it to the on side for a single
not his most convincing boundary, he made room and got an outside edge, no slip and just beat a diving short third man
clips it down to deep square leg for a single
lovely timing! He clipped it close to his pads expecting to get not more than a couple, Cheema was tested at deep midwicket but he had no chance
fires it full outside the off stump and he drive that wide of cover, Azam does well in the deep to cut it off
tossed up on middle and leg, he tucked it to deep midwicket
this one straightens and he comes forward and drives to the off side
stays back and knocks to towards long-on
Tendulkar gets across to the off stump and sweeps him to deep square leg
